    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2026-03-02"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "1970-01-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>, <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/37f42bb3-86ca-4420-a71d-41a2d4ea7457> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> _:b0__87599.
_:b0__87599 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((11.24 69.09,26.06 69.09,26.06 55.03,11.24 55.03,11.24 69.09))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
