<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/38cd8070-ef36-455b-bdfe-5b39c152e4a1> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> _:b0__25623.
_:b0__25623 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((11.50 75.10,51.60 75.10,51.60 42.40,11.50 42.40,11.50 75.10))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/38cd8070-ef36-455b-bdfe-5b39c152e4a1> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://www.smhi.se/data/utforskaren-oppna-data/klimatolog_smhi.se>;
