<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#4b48ff54241520f528586055c72ea9c4>.
<#4b48ff54241520f528586055c72ea9c4> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N85541>;
