_:b0__6839 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Källa: SKR:s personal- och lönestatistik (novemberstatistiken)."@sv;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement>.
<http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N11201> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-04-11"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
