<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#09c10be07147725c071c9d864866b86f>.
<#09c10be07147725c071c9d864866b86f> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U31004>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-02T06:19:05.810Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
