}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#567edd49d0d5977808519d3d7a2045c1>.
<#567edd49d0d5977808519d3d7a2045c1> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N85532>;
