_:b0__3789 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Källa: SCB:s Räkenskapssammandrag."@sv;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement>.
<http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N40010> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-08-28"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Nettokostnad flyktingmottagande, kr/inv"@sv;
