    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement>.
<http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N15063> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-08-28"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Övriga kostnader i kommunal grundskola F-9, kr/elev"@sv;
