<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#ab79a7eb29a5033762388fff46cd9290>.
<#ab79a7eb29a5033762388fff46cd9290> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N45904>;
