<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#e9cc80ce8a625c79174ed7cffdb990c1>.
<#e9cc80ce8a625c79174ed7cffdb990c1> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U17450>;
