<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#05b703ce6bff67937529a2f73585e4c8>.
<#05b703ce6bff67937529a2f73585e4c8> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N20900>;
