<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#b32dd42dcc5478dd33a7ed8684f399e9>.
<#b32dd42dcc5478dd33a7ed8684f399e9> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U23495>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-02T06:19:05.949Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
