<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#fe944b4bbba73bc54c560d22d9656c4f>.
<#fe944b4bbba73bc54c560d22d9656c4f> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N85066>;
