    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2015-09-18"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://doi.org/10.5879/ecds/2016-07-07.2/1> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
